metadata.description:
Genesis  
Herbal Medicine SeedPod:  
Tropical Savanna Climate  
0.2860

Planetary Medicine SeedPods contain seeds of PERP certified medicinal plants for intentional use by specialized herbalists. These Pods comprise a selection of seeds which sprout into plants with therapeutic effects for human and animal kin. 

This Herbal Medicine SeedPod is developed specifically for Tropical Savanna areas, and includes seeds from the Baobab Tree, Frankincense, Caju. For best results, deploy under the first full moon of Spring.
